* Fixed a bug where macOS app bundles embedded inside another app (e.g., login helpers at `Contents/Library/LoginItems/` or framework helpers at `Contents/Frameworks/`) were collected as separate software entries. When these embedded bundles shared the same `bundle_identifier` as the parent app, they could claim the software title name (e.g., "AmphetamineLoginHelper" instead of "Amphetamine"). Embedded bundles are now filtered out at both the osquery query level and during Go-side ingestion.
